00:01:32.850 --> 00:01:38.890
Ji tikrai tyra moteris ar ne.“

00:01:39.430 --> 00:01:43.140
Taigi jie visi nusileido kaip „sadhai“,

00:01:43.310 --> 00:01:47.100
